Source: mqtt-cpp
Version: 10.0.0
Description: Header-only MQTT client/server for C++14 based on Boost.Asio.
Homepage: https://github.com/redboltz/mqtt_cpp
Build-Depends: boost-any, boost-asio, boost-multi-index, boost-program-options, boost-system, boost-type-erasure, boost-units

Feature: log
Description: Output log messages using Boost::Log
Build-Depends: boost-log

Feature: tls
Description: Support for TLS
Build-Depends: openssl

Feature: ws
Description: Support for Websockets
Build-Depends: boost-beast
